data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juli 17, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104fgi1689059963417.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/fgi1689059963417.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/fgi1689059963417.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"fgi1689059963417\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">If specified, this option suppresses the default message and sends an asynchronous\n\t\tmessage to the Uniface application, enabling it to provide customized handling of the\n\t\texpiration notice.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"fgi1689059963417__p_d141092e1_d141093e1_d141094e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">LM_NOTIFICATION_POSTMESSAGE</code>{<code class=\"ph codeph\">=T</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">true</code>\n\t\t\t| <code class=\"ph codeph\">Y</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">yes</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">1</code> }</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"fgi1689059963417__p_d141095e1_d141096e1_d141097e1\">The message that is sent has the following\n\t\t\tproperties:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"fgi1689059963417__ul_j51_ywb_xvb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"fgi1689059963417__li_d49829e1_d49830e1_d49831e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">$msgsrc: \"UNIFACE\"</code>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"fgi1689059963417__li_d49832e1_d49833e1_d49834e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">$msgid: \"LICENSING\"</code>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"fgi1689059963417__li_d49835e1_d49836e1_d49837e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">$msgdata:</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">UnifaceList</var>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"fgi1689059963417__p_d141098e1_d141099e1_d141100e1\">The <var class=\"keyword varname\">UnifaceList</var> contains the\n\t\t\tfollowing items:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"fgi1689059963417__ul_l51_ywb_xvb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"fgi1689059963417__li_d49838e1_d49839e1_d49840e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">LICMGR</code>—license manager used: <code class=\"ph codeph\">Sentinel</code>. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"fgi1689059963417__li_d49841e1_d49842e1_d49843e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">FEATURE</code>—license feature abbreviation, for example\n\t\t\t\t\t<code class=\"ph codeph\">UDE</code>. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"fgi1689059963417__li_d49844e1_d49845e1_d49846e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">REASON</code>—reason for the message: <code class=\"ph codeph\">license</code>,\n\t\t\t\t\t<code class=\"ph codeph\">lease</code>, <code class=\"ph codeph\">version</code>\n<span class=\"ph\">, <code class=\"ph codeph\">grace</code>,\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<code class=\"ph codeph\">maintenance</code>, <code class=\"ph codeph\">no_more_maintenance</code>, or\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<code class=\"ph codeph\">commuter</code></span>. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"fgi1689059963417__li_d49847e1_d49848e1_d49849e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">DAYSLEFT</code>—the number of days that the feature is still valid\n\t\t\t\t\t(<code class=\"ph codeph\">license</code>), the number of days a grace license is defined to be\n\t\t\t\tvalid (<code class=\"ph codeph\">grace</code>), or the number of days the maintenance contract is\n\t\t\t\tstill valid (<code class=\"ph codeph\">maintenance</code> and <code class=\"ph codeph\">no_more_maintenance</code>).\n\t\t\t\tIn the case of <code class=\"ph codeph\">no_more_maintenace</code>, this number is negative. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"fgi1689059963417__li_d49850e1_d49851e1_d49852e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">HOURSLEFT</code>—number of hours left a grace license is still valid.\n\t\t\t</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"fgi1689059963417__note_w468ab1b5c11c15_w469ab1b5c11_w470ab1b5_w471ab1\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span>  In the case of a\n\t\t\tcommuter license, when a commuter license is about to expire, two messages are send. One\n\t\t\twith <code class=\"ph codeph\">REASON</code>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">'license'</code> and another with <code class=\"ph codeph\">REASON</code>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">'commuter'</code>. Only one of these needs to be handled. For example, if you\n\t\t\thandle the message with <code class=\"ph codeph\">REASON</code>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">'license'</code>, you do not need to handle the message with reason\n\t\t\t\t<code class=\"ph codeph\">'commuter'</code>.</div>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_4398094\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_4398094\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "LM_NOTIFICATION_POSTMESSAGE Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juli 17, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 If specified, this option suppresses the default message and sends an asynchronous message to the Uniface application, enabling it to provide customized handling of the expiration notice. LM_NOTIFICATION_POSTMESSAGE { =T | true | Y | yes | 1 } The message that is sent has the following properties: $msgsrc: \"UNIFACE\" $msgid: \"LICENSING\" $msgdata: UnifaceList The UnifaceList contains the following items: LICMGR —license manager used: Sentinel . FEATURE —license feature abbreviation, for example UDE . REASON —reason for the message: license , lease , version , grace , maintenance , no_more_maintenance , or commuter . DAYSLEFT —the number of days that the feature is still valid ( license ), the number of days a grace license is defined to be valid ( grace ), or the number of days the maintenance contract is still valid ( maintenance and no_more_maintenance ). In the case of no_more_maintenace , this number is negative. HOURSLEFT —number of hours left a grace license is still valid. Note: In the case of a commuter license, when a commuter license is about to expire, two messages are send. One with REASON 'license' and another with REASON 'commuter' . Only one of these needs to be handled. For example, if you handle the message with REASON 'license' , you do not need to handle the message with reason 'commuter' . Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}